## Tagging

Table `tags` indexed by UUID

Implement a macro for showing an image

Show tags when showing a picture 

Have a /tag/foo/1/ page for paging a specific tag

Clicking on a tags brings you to the appropriate tags page

Endpoint /tag for showing the available tags

How to add a tag? On the /edit/<uuid> page

Tags > dropdown menu in the top?
